question: Within a radius of 50 kilometers, where can I find  a fast food restaurant along the way to Boston Marathon Finish Line, Boston, MA from TownePlace Suites, Wrentham, MA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.312415 42.038711)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.078616 42.349751)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.312415 42.038711)',4326)::geography, 50000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.312415 42.038711)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.description: Menu at https://places.singleplatform.com/greco-11/menu Available on some food delivery services.

[4].display_name: Boston Marathon Finish Line, Boston, MA
